metadata.name: Yilki Horses
metadata.description:
Galloping through the fields, Ali Kemer, the shepherd of the Yılkı horses of Kayseri  is chasing the band of horses . The thuds of thousands o shores moving together lifts the ground and are shrouded in a blanket of dust creating a spectacular shot of the cowboy in the background wrangling the band of horses .

Edition: 1/1 

Title: Band of Horses 

Artist: Kirangovind.eth


Location: Kayseri, Turkey
